metadata.name: Chasing Paradise (w slenderbodies)
metadata.description: Chasing Paradise is the first single off of my third EP Glass House. I wrote and produced this song in a "Glass House" in Malibu during my Daniel Allan & Friends writing camp - a result of a crowdfund spearheaded by myself and Henry Chatfield which led to 64 total demos and the 4-track Glass House EP.
